a good example for everyone,

00:02:31.359 --> 00:02:33.862 position:50% align:center
but you're so
undisciplined! Do better!

00:02:33.945 --> 00:02:35.280 position:50% align:center
[MIYUKI groans]

00:02:35.363 --> 00:02:38.241 position:50% align:center
[KAGUYA]
Iino, a word?

00:02:38.324 --> 00:02:39.701 position:50% align:center
You're only a first-year,

00:02:39.784 --> 00:02:41.786 position:50% align:center
so you may not understand
how the president operates.

00:02:41.870 --> 00:02:43.163 position:50% align:center
But one thing he does faithfully

00:02:43.246 --> 00:02:45.582 position:50% align:center
is set a proper
precedent for us.

00:02:45.665 --> 00:02:47.792 position:50% align:center
I'd appreciate it if
you stopped judging him.

00:02:47.876 --> 00:02:49.669 position:50% align:center
