not good behavior.

00:02:54.382 --> 00:02:56.301 position:50% align:center
Iino, you misunderstood.

00:02:56.384 --> 00:02:58.386 position:50% align:center
I get that you like
each other a lot,

00:02:58.470 --> 00:03:00.180 position:50% align:center
