that we need to see!

00:03:00.263 --> 00:03:02.932 position:50% align:center
[KAGUYA gasps]
You think we like each other?

00:03:03.016 --> 00:03:05.143 position:50% align:center
Wow. Who knew we
came across that way?

00:03:05.226 --> 00:03:07.937 position:50% align:center
