letting it get the best of you!

00:03:08.021 --> 00:03:10.023 position:50% align:center
I wonder how far love can go.

00:03:10.106 --> 00:03:11.649 position:50% align:center
[KAGUYA]
She's such a sweetheart!

00:03:11.733 --> 00:03:14.402 position:50% align:center
[MIKO] Bottom line, the next
time one of you misbehaves,

00:03:14.486 --> 00:03:16.071 position:50% align:center
I'm using my
authority as a member of

00:03:16.154 --> 00:03:18.531 position:50% align:center
the Disciplinary Committee
to put you in your place!

00:03:18.615 --> 00:03:19.783 position:50% align:center
You know...

00:03:19.866 --> 00:03:22.660 position:50% align:center
...you catch more flies
with honey than vinegar.

00:03:22.744 --> 00:03:25.163 position:50% align:center
I don't care if you're a
stickler for the rules or what.

00:03:25.246 --> 00:03:27.123 position:50% align:center
You need to grasp the
concept that the people

00:03:27.207 --> 00:03:29.501 position:50% align:center
you're cracking down on
have feelings, too.

00:03:29.584 --> 00:03:30.585 position:50% align:center
