00:05:05.847 --> 00:05:08.350 position:50% align:center
Not getting mad is
only making me madder!

00:05:08.433 --> 00:05:10.977 position:50% align:center
[CHIKA]
Ah, in that case...

00:05:11.061 --> 00:05:12.437 position:50% align:center
